- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with classifying user-generated text and personal pictures.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with analyzing personal pictures for user profiling.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is relevant as the paper discusses user profiling in the context of social media companies.
